A: Topic category — politics, environment, personal, workplace, historical etc, Lens used — which angle was chosen, Toxicity score — input and output rated 0 to 10, Guardrail triggered — yes/no and which layer, Shift score — did the user indicate something changed, Geographic data — country and state only, no city or finer, Output Quality Score

Q: Where does this data go — who sees it?

A: An internal dashboard — team only



